abstract: Former Pres George W Bush and hundreds of others gather at Capitol to pay tribute to former Vice Pres Dick Cheney as his official bust, carved in marble, is unveiled.
lead_paragraph: Former President George W. Bush led the many Republicans attending the unveiling of a bust of his vice president; few Democrats were there.

headline.main: Tribute and a Reunion for Dick Cheney in Capital
